### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### REMOTE UPLOAD — POST /uploads (por provider)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Remote upload — DoodStream
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "episodeId": "{{episodeId}}",
  "provider": "DOODSTREAM",
  "sourceType": "REMOTE_URL",
  "sourceUrl": "https://www.cartoonsarea.cc/USER-DATA/Cartoonsarea/Japines%20Language/T/Tensei%20Shitara%20Slime%20Datta%20Ken/Season%201/Episode%201//01%20The%20Storm%20Dragon,%20Veldora.mp4"
}

### Remote upload — MixDrop
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "episodeId": "{{episodeId}}",
  "provider": "MIXDROP",
  "sourceType": "REMOTE_URL",
  "sourceUrl": "https://www.cartoonsarea.cc/USER-DATA/Cartoonsarea/Japines%20Language/T/Tensei%20Shitara%20Slime%20Datta%20Ken/Season%201/Episode%201//01%20The%20Storm%20Dragon,%20Veldora.mp4"
}

### Remote upload — Streamtape
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "episodeId": "{{episodeId}}",
  "provider": "STREAMTAPE",
  "sourceType": "REMOTE_URL",
  "sourceUrl": "https://www.cartoonsarea.cc/USER-DATA/Cartoonsarea/Japines%20Language/N/Naruto/Season%201/Episode%204//04%20Pass%20or%20Fail%20Survival%20Test.mp4"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### STREAM UPLOAD — POST /uploads/stream (por provider)
### El server recibe el archivo en memoria y lo forwarda al provider.
### La API key nunca llega al cliente.
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Stream upload — DoodStream
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="episodeId"

{{episodeId}}
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="provider"

DOODSTREAM
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="episode-01.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< /path/to/local/video.mp4
--boundary--

### Stream upload — MixDrop
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="episodeId"

{{episodeId}}
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="provider"

MIXDROP
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="episode-01.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< /path/to/local/video.mp4
--boundary--

### Stream upload — Streamtape
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/stream
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="episodeId"

{{episodeId}}
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="provider"

STREAMTAPE
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="episode-01.mp4"
Content-Type: video/mp4

< /path/to/local/video.mp4
--boundary--

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### PRESIGN UPLOAD — POST /uploads/presign
### Solo Streamtape soporta presign seguro (sin secrets).
### DoodStream y MixDrop retornan error (usar /uploads/stream).
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Presign upload — Streamtape (seguro, sin secrets)
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/presign
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "episodeId": "{{episodeId}}",
  "provider": "STREAMTAPE"
}

### Presign upload — DoodStream (retorna error, usar /uploads/stream)
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/presign
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "episodeId": "{{episodeId}}",
  "provider": "DOODSTREAM"
}

### Presign upload — MixDrop (retorna error, no soporta presign)
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/presign
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "episodeId": "{{episodeId}}",
  "provider": "MIXDROP"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### CONFIRM UPLOAD — POST /uploads/confirm (por provider)
### Después de subir directo al provider via presign, registrar el resultado.
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Confirm upload — DoodStream
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "episodeId": "{{episodeId}}",
  "provider": "DOODSTREAM",
  "providerFileId": "FILECODE_FROM_PROVIDER",
  "embedUrl": "https://dood.to/e/FILECODE_FROM_PROVIDER"
}

### Confirm upload — MixDrop
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "episodeId": "{{episodeId}}",
  "provider": "MIXDROP",
  "providerFileId": "FILEREF_FROM_PROVIDER",
  "embedUrl": "https://mixdrop.co/e/FILEREF_FROM_PROVIDER"
}

### Confirm upload — Streamtape
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "episodeId": "{{episodeId}}",
  "provider": "STREAMTAPE",
  "providerFileId": "FILEID_FROM_PROVIDER",
  "embedUrl": "https://streamtape.com/e/FILEID_FROM_PROVIDER"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### BULK UPLOAD — POST /uploads/bulk (por provider)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Bulk upload — DoodStream
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "DOODSTREAM",
  "items": [
    { "episodeId": "REPLACE_WITH_EP_UUID_1", "url": "https://example.com/ep1.mp4" },
    { "episodeId": "REPLACE_WITH_EP_UUID_2", "url": "https://example.com/ep2.mp4" },
    { "episodeId": "REPLACE_WITH_EP_UUID_3", "url": "https://example.com/ep3.mp4" }
  ]
}

### Bulk upload — MixDrop
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "MIXDROP",
  "items": [
    { "episodeId": "REPLACE_WITH_EP_UUID_1", "url": "https://example.com/ep1.mp4" },
    { "episodeId": "REPLACE_WITH_EP_UUID_2", "url": "https://example.com/ep2.mp4" }
  ]
}

### Bulk upload — Streamtape
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "STREAMTAPE",
  "items": [
    { "episodeId": "REPLACE_WITH_EP_UUID_1", "url": "https://example.com/ep1.mp4" },
    { "episodeId": "REPLACE_WITH_EP_UUID_2", "url": "https://example.com/ep2.mp4" }
  ]
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### CSV UPLOAD — POST /uploads/csv (por provider)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### CSV upload — DoodStream
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/csv?provider=DOODSTREAM
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="uploads.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

anime_slug,episode_number,url
naruto,1,https://example.com/naruto-01.mp4
naruto,2,https://example.com/naruto-02.mp4
naruto,3,https://example.com/naruto-03.mp4

--boundary--

### CSV upload — MixDrop
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/csv?provider=MIXDROP
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="uploads.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

anime_slug,episode_number,url
naruto,1,https://example.com/naruto-01.mp4
naruto,2,https://example.com/naruto-02.mp4

--boundary--

### CSV upload — Streamtape
POST {{baseUrl}}/uploads/csv?provider=STREAMTAPE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="uploads.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

anime_slug,episode_number,url
naruto,1,https://example.com/naruto-01.mp4
naruto,2,https://example.com/naruto-02.mp4

--boundary--

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
### JOBS — Listar y consultar estado
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List upload jobs (uploader sees own, admin sees all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/uploads/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get specific upload job
GET {{baseUrl}}/uploads/jobs/REPLACE_WITH_JOB_UUID
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
